msgstr "PDF girdisinin bazı kısıtlamaları:"

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:736
msgid "Complex, multi-column, and image based documents are not supported."
msgstr "Karmaşık, çok-sütunlu, ve resim temelli belgeler desteklenmez."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:737
msgid ""
"Extraction of vector images and tables from within the document is also not "
